        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/25930571/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/25930571/" class="">第67页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/49542325/" class=" " title="埃里克·布莱尔">埃里克·布莱尔</a>
                (bu)
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="25930571">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">Walter Bagehot:one cannot judge the consequences of any reform until the generation in which was present has left the scene.</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-04-22 16:35</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">1人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                Walter Bagehot:<blockquote><q>one cannot judge the consequences of any reform until the generation in which was present has left the scene.</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
</span>
</div>

                  </div>
                <div class="pl col-time">
                  <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/25930571/#comments">回应</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
                  2013-04-22 16:35
                </div>
              </div>
